  new Date(a.created_at).getTime() - new Date(b.created_at).getTime()
);
```

**UI Layout (RTL Hebrew):**
```
[Conversations List - 30% width] | [Messages Panel - 70% width]
```

**Messages Panel:**
- Messages flow from top (oldest) to bottom (newest)
- New messages auto-scroll into view at bottom
- Date separators between days
- Message bubbles aligned:
  - **Customer**: Right-aligned, light background
  - **Agent/Owner**: Left-aligned, WhatsApp green background
  - **Agent messages** have "🤖" icon indicator

### 3. Key UI Interactions

**Scroll Behavior:**
- Messages panel: Auto-scroll to bottom when new message arrives
- Conversations list: Maintain scroll position when selecting different conversation
- Infinite scroll for message history (load older messages when scrolling up)

**Real-time Updates:**
- New messages should appear immediately via Supabase Realtime
- Conversation list reorders automatically when `updated_at` changes
- Visual indicator (green dot) for new unread messages

