- Message content supports Hebrew text, emojis, and RTL mixed with LTR
- Date formatting: Hebrew locale (יום שלישי, 12 במרץ)

### 5. Accessibility Considerations

- **Screen readers**: Announce "new message from [contact]" when messages arrive
- **Keyboard navigation**: Tab through conversations, Enter to select, Arrow keys to navigate messages
- **Focus management**: When new message arrives, focus doesn't shift unless user is actively in that conversation
- **Color contrast**: Ensure message text meets WCAG AA on both background colors

